  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK110">
<l>ennaṉṟi koṉṟārkku muyvuṇṭā muyvillai</l>
<l>ceynnaṉṟi koṉṟa makaṟku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even for those who've killed every good thing, there is liberation—but not</l>
<l>for a son who's killed the good things done for him.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
